options_desc.fullscreen: Set the game in fullscreen or not.
options_desc.hitboxes: Show or hide Hitboxes for player, enemies and projectiles.

meta_words.teleport: Teleports the user to the mouse.

affliction_desc.fury: Grants 15% more physical damage. This effect can stack.
affliction_desc.bleed: Inflicts physical damage every seconds that ignores defenses.

spells_desc.voidbolt:
Shoot a flurry of void spheres, dealing
minor void damage.
spells_desc.arc:
Release a seeking lightning bolt,
dealing minor thunder damage and chaining 3 times.
spells_desc.firebolt:
Shoot a firebolt toward the mouse, dealing 
fire damage.
spells_desc.firebolt2: Kinda like firebolt but not quite so ...
spells_desc.icebolt:
Creates a barrage of ice spears that deals
major ice damage in a straight line,
piercing enemies.
spells_desc.exult:
This spell cannot be cast.
Upon inflicting a critical hit, release a bloody shockwave.
spells_desc.elefury:
Unleash the fury of the elements, increasing
elemental damage dealt.
spells_desc.wdash:
Quickly dashes in the direction of your movement
and increase your movement speed.
spells_desc.fslash:
Delivers a powerful melee attack.
Reusing the attack in a short delay
greatly increase its damage.
spells_desc.fireball:
Launch a powerful fireball toward the mouse
dealing medium fire damage.
On contact, creates a powerful explosion.
spells_desc.masterstrike:
Deliver a serie a quick blows.
The third strike is a guaranteed critical hit.

blank: Removes all modifiers from an item.
thurisaz: Transform a blank item into a rare item, adding 3 to 6 modifiers.
ansuz:
Adds a random modifier to an item.
Blank items can have one modifier, Enchanted items two,
Blessed up to 6 and Exalted up to 8.
ingwaz: Reroll all values of the modifiers on an item.
othalan:
Seals a random modifier of an item, making it impossible to change.
This rune can only be used on items with no seals.
uruz: Either exalts a blessed item or destroy it.
raido: Changes the modifiers of a blessed item.
algiz: Randomly changes the modifiers of an enchanted item.
